text: Taylor Swift announced her eighth studio album, “Folklore,” without advance promotion, catching fans and the music business off guard. The album and her new music video, “Cardigan,” are due Thursday night. https://t.co/Ci0UCmbxit

text: China’s Communist Party expelled an influential businessman who in an essay excoriated leader Xi Jinping for his handling of the coronavirus pandemic and attacked his domineering style and intolerance for criticism https://t.co/o7388hav0u

name: WSJ
text: The owner of Ebony magazine is being forced into bankruptcy by creditors who say they want to take over the publication, which has chronicled Black culture for 75 years but has declined since being sold by its founding publisher https://t.co/6BU61Yfd7g
